  <brief_title>Safety And Efficacy Of Rifabutin In Patients For Non-HIV Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Special Investigation For Non-hiv Patients Of Mycobutin (Regulatory Post Marketing Commitment Plan).</official_title>
  <sponsors>
